rule EvasionBypass {
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass detection via skipped jumps"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 8B 45 FF 75 08 E8 C8 FF FF FF }   // Surrounding context around a key jump
        $pattern1 = { 6A 5A FF 75 08 FF 15 AC B0 41 00 }   // Another critical jump path
        $pattern2 = { 00 B9 A9 D3 E8 0B 00 00 00 FF 75 08 FF 15 8C E1 BA 00 }  // Complex exit path pattern
}

    condition:
        any of them
}
